@chapter Overview
DoorBot is a Minecraft bot built using Mineflayer that specializes in door interactions.

@chapter Features
@section Movement
@itemize
@item Basic movement controls
@item Pathfinding
@item Door traversal
@item other interactions like a jump Bed interaction
@end itemize

@section Commands
@table @code
@item gotobed
Find and move to nearest bed
@item gotodoor
Find and interact with nearest door
@item come
Move to player's location
@item test
Run test sequence
@item stop
Shutdown bot
@end table

@bye 